headline: AM Best Affirms Credit Ratings of CVS Health Corporation’s Aetna Inc. Subsidiaries
summary: OLDWICK, N.J., May 08, 2025--AM Best has affirmed the Financial Strength Rating (FSR) of A (Excellent) and the Long-Term Issuer Credit Ratings (Long-Term ICRs) of "a" (Excellent) of Aetna Life Insurance Company (ALIC) (Hartford, CT) and the other members of Aetna Health & Life Group, which are operating entities of Aetna Inc. (Aetna) and wholly owned subsidiaries of CVS Health Corporation (CVS Health) [NYSE: CVS]. (Please see below for a detailed listing of the companies.)
